Helena Rasche, Anthony Bretaudeau, and Mateo Boudet (2019), `Galaxy Apollo Tools <https://github.com/galaxy-genome-annotation/galaxy-tools/tree/master/tools/apollo>`_
]]>
    </token>
</macros>
